fields.indexing_notes: Two sets of foliation occur in this manuscript.  Small Arabic numerals in the upper-right-hand corners of the rectos appear on some folios, but not all (either not photographed or trimmed).  On this folio (28r in the Arabic system), a large lower-case Roman "i" appears in the centre of the top margin (coinciding with the beginning of the commune sanctorum).
